column1: Hey! Just moved to New York. Excited to be here!
Can we meet tomorrow at 5 pm?
My phone number changed, it's now 555-123-4567.
I live at 1234 Maple St., Anytown, USA.
Let's catch up over the weekend.
What time is our meeting scheduled for?
My birthday is next month on the 20th.
We should organize a party for next Saturday.
